text: The 1912 TCU Horned Frogs football team represented Texas Christian University (TCU) in the 1912 college football season. The Horned Frogs finished the season 8–1 overall. The team was coached by Willis T. Stewart in his first and only year as head coach. The Frogs played their home games in Fort Worth, Texas. ==Schedule== ==References== TCU Category:TCU Horned Frogs football seasons TCU Horned Frogs football
